No matter how old I get, this will always always always hold a very special place in my heart♥️

Honestly, if you would have told 22 year old Bhavika, she will one day come in a Dove commercial, she would have loved her ass off. 

So once again, a BIG THANK YOU and a virtual hug for you all♥️♥️

1. The way you squeeze out the water from your hair matters a lot. Rubbing them only makes them crazy and make them be overtime. Hence, you should always try to treat them very, very gently when they are wet.

2. Using a bond repair product can make a big difference in the way your hair look. They can make your hair shiny, soft, frizz-free and manageable as well. Currently I’m using the @raisebeautyindia bond repaid cream and a small amount is enough to make my hair super soft.

3. Hair Growth Serums are a non-negotiable for me now. They help keep my hairfall im check, scalp in good health and hair growing fast. Currently using @bareanatomy.haircare SCALP serum. It actually has some amazing ingredients. Before you ask, the texture is water-like and doesn’t weigh down my hair at all.

4. Blow drying over air drying was a tip internet game me and I’m all for it now. I do not have to spend all day drying my hair and still end up with frizzy hair. Blowdry truly helps in reducing the phrase and making my hair a lot more manageable. Using @dyson_india
